Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.80,0:00:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Ryota-san, don't be so cold!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.38,0:00:26.59,Top,,0,0,0,,Told you already, no dice.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.53,Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, take us for a ride, will ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.53,0:00:32.10,Top,,0,0,0,,You've got nothing better to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.10,0:00:35.96,Top,,0,0,0,,We're your only passengers anyway. \NPerfect timing, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.96,0:00:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This month, I've been flooded with complaints. \NIf I don't drive properly, I'm screwed.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.77,0:00:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say boring stuff like that.\NJust floor it for once! Let's go wild!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.61,0:00:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's been pissing me off lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.17,0:00:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, take us somewhere quiet.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.79,0:00:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You could use a little fun yourself, \Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.58,0:00:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ryota-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.54,0:01:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe that's not such a bad idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.08,0:01:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A passenger?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.48,0:01:19.73,Top,,0,0,0,,Yo, long time no see, Takao.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.73,0:01:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Otaki! Otaki, that you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.15,0:01:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, please, Ryota-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.96,0:01:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The ladies are asking you nicely, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.32,0:01:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Karuizawa sounds perfect. \NIt's settled. Let's hit a motel in Karuizawa!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.78,0:01:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You little brats! {lit: rotten women}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.64,0:01:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,High schoolers puffing cigarettes, \Ntalking about motels.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.09,0:01:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have a shred of decency left?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.42,0:01:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, drop the act, grandpa. {lit: [talking] so big}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.40,0:01:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukari, you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.49,0:01:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.80,0:01:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell's your problem, bastard?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.31,0:01:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.56,0:02:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Otaki!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.94,0:02:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez. I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.27,0:02:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When did girls start talking like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.40,0:02:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Everywhere I go, it's the same:\Nsloppy, careless, vulgar women!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.49,0:02:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Greasy hair, black teeth,\N and nose hair flying!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.91,0:02:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumb as bricks, \Nspitting like some unknown weapon! {talking specifically about saliva here; no clue what's the deal with unknown weapon, maybe it's actually "perfectly calm"}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.18,0:02:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing they know how to move \Nis their hips in bed!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.08,0:02:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this kind of women...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.36,0:02:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,gets this! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.49,0:02:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking trash like you might become mothers one day... It's terrifying! Take that!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.87,0:02:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This country's going to hell!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.52,0:02:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{Take it! Take it! Take it!}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.75,0:02:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop it, Otaki!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.86,0:02:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This medicine is bitter. {lit: it's good - meaning "let me do it, I'm doing the right thing"}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.29,0:02:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,With girls like that, you gotta teach them \Nwith your fists! That's the only way they learn! {lit: unless it's with body, they won't understand}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.90,0:02:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I said stop it, damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.93,0:03:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the fuck out!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.81,0:03:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, Takao...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.24,0:03:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're even wasting time\N on girls like that now?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.26,0:03:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too lenient!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.17,0:03:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Women are all like that. Treat them too nice, \Nand they'll climb all over you. {tsukiageru}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.13,0:03:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch yourself. \NDon't go drawing the short straw. {literal}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.73,0:03:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshimoto, summer's almost here. \NTime to get out and feel free again!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.14,0:03:29.56,Top,,0,0,0,,This year, I swear I'll score on the beach.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.55,0:03:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right. Good luck with that.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.47,0:03:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you're no fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.70,0:03:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.07,0:03:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Yukari and Megumi over there?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.87,0:03:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you two?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.66,0:03:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor things, you look \Nlike you've been through hell.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.54,0:03:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How about I take you to a hotel \Nand make you feel better, huh? {nursing; looking after}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.65,0:03:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, girls fighting in public \Nis just pathetic. Cut it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.53,0:03:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it! It was a guy who did this!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.19,0:03:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.61,0:04:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.39,0:04:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you two take care of him, \NI'll let you take me out! {Was "... let you have a go at me", but that sounded too much like they were going to fight.}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Megumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.79,0:04:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. We'll just use them \Nand ditch them after, simple as that. {to feign ignorance/to evade one's responsibilities}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.28,0:04:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.05,0:04:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's that pathetic guy hiding?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.82,0:04:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We... will... tear him apart!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.18,0:04:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Otaki-san's in town?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.17,0:04:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He was just on my bus earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.84,0:04:32.00,Top,,0,0,0,,E-Earlier... and where'd he go after that?! {/but where is he now}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.15,0:04:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He was gonna grab a drink with me,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.36,0:04:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but when he saw a group of delinquent girls \Nnear Third Street, he hopped off. {ズベ公}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.18,0:04:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Street?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.22,0:04:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right around the corner!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.02,0:04:49.62,Top,,0,0,0,,Why are you freaking out, Taka-chan? \NWho is this Otaki guy anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.04,0:04:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.46,0:04:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When Otaki-san shows up, \Ndon't you dare cross your legs or act loose!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.80,0:04:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your mouth too!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.95,0:05:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy'll smack any girl who acts sloppy \Nor talks back, no hesitation!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.97,0:05:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So act like a proper lady, got it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.73,0:05:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Why the hell should I change for him?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.27,0:05:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If he tries to hit me, \Nyou'd better protect me, Taka!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.32,0:05:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.05,0:05:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! You're my boyfriend, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.36,0:05:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm saying this for your own good, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.66,0:05:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So will you protect me or not?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.25,0:05:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He was always rough with women,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.55,0:05:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but today, he was out of his mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he just woke up \Non the wrong side of the bed.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.86,0:05:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, once he sets his eyes \Non a girl he doesn't like,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.93,0:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,he won't calm down \Nuntil he's hit her a few times.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.74,0:05:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's glaring at you, \Nexpect at least three punches.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.22,0:05:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! That's him! That's the guy!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.66,0:05:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No mistake?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.47,0:05:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.10,0:05:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you better let me have my turn after.\N A deal's a deal.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.61,0:05:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, I got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.12,0:06:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now get going!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.13,0:06:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.59,0:06:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Hold it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you prick!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.98,0:06:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's you two!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.85,0:06:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?! \NThat's him! That's the guy!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and take him down!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.23,0:06:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You spoiled women!{/broad/whore} \NDon't talk like that in front of Otaki-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.12,0:06:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Act more ladylike, damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.26,0:06:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, women these days are hopeless!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.56,0:06:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.39,0:06:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Otaki-san, when did you get here?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.12,0:06:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How did it come to this?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.69,0:06:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to leave?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.90,0:06:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, that guy's not normal! \NIt's dangerous!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.02,0:06:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are stubborn, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.85,0:06:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, Takao's here too?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.02,0:06:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who I ran into by chance.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.08,0:06:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi, you doing well?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.11,0:07:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Been a while, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to see you're still\N in one piece, Otaki-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.36,0:07:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And who's this girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.89,0:07:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that skirt. I can practically see her panties.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.29,0:07:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's your problem?!\N It's none of your business, you moron!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.46,0:07:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.68,0:07:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please, Otaki-san, go easy on her!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.73,0:07:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my girlfriend! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.05,0:07:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's your job to make sure she's raised right!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.10,0:07:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way! We can't let you lay a finger on Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.49,0:07:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Even you, Otaki-san, \Ncan't get away with that!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.17,0:07:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan's one of the few girls \Nwe can actually talk to like normal people!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.89,0:07:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't stand by\N while someone hurts her!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.74,0:07:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.08,0:07:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When summer comes, Yuki-chan doesn't mind wearing light clothes around us, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.77,0:08:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll cross her legs just right\N so we get a peek.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.88,0:08:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes she doesn't wear a bra, \Nso you can see her nipples! {?????? i assume that pocchin no ari is nipple}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.30,0:08:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,On sleepless nights, \Nshe's been a real lifesaver! {meaning they jerked off to her image in their imagination}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.66,0:08:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You might not get it, Otaki-san,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.13,0:08:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but to us, she's special.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.56,0:08:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let anyone hurt her!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.03,0:08:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Otaki, what the hell's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.96,0:08:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to be the kind of guy who could see \Nthe good in women before the bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.91,0:08:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you punks...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.99,0:08:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep putting women on a pedestal,\N you'll end up crying later.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.52,0:08:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to drill it into them that a woman's supposed to obey a man from the get-go. {lit: hammer it into them [with fists]}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.84,0:08:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Spoil them, and they'll just walk all over you! {tsukiageru animals - w/e that means, probably "creatures"}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.53,0:08:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys don't understand a damn thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.93,0:08:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.71,0:09:03.87,Top,,0,0,0,,Why the hell are you skipping \Nyour work at the factory, honey? {I assume this koujo is some factory he works at and not takashi's auto shop}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.20,0:09:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mizue... How'd you find me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.51,0:09:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anywhere you'd be struttin' around \Nacting big, it'd be this town.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.95,0:09:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Otaki! You're married?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.75,0:09:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry! Forgive me, dear! \NI skipped work today! I won't do it again!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.25,0:09:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.70,0:09:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I told the foreman you'd take the night shift, \Nso you'll work straight through. No sleep, got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.18,0:09:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am! \NI'll work! I swear, honey!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.11,0:09:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sorry for the scene, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.88,0:09:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now move it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.61,0:09:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, I get it. \NPlease don't be angry no more... {???????}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.18,0:09:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, are we going home? {???????}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.68,0:09:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.28,0:10:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, it's hot as hell today.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.01,0:10:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go walking outside, \Nwe'd melt right into the asphalt.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.85,0:10:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I could go for a trip to the beach.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.83,0:10:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The beach, huh? Maybe we could invite \NTajima-san or Yoshimoto-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.78,0:10:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You kidding, Megumi?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.63,0:10:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather stand under the blazing sun \Nthan go with those two.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.31,0:10:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, guess so.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.97,0:10:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what they're always after anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.12,0:10:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.68,0:10:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Ryota-san could take us instead.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.61,0:10:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy won't lift a finger \Nunless he's in the mood. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.74,0:10:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's it!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.58,0:10:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We just gotta get him in the mood, Yukari!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.80,0:11:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.29,0:11:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Whisper, whisper, whisper...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.12,0:11:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.46,0:11:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to do {\i1}that{\i0}? \NIt's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.67,0:11:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just trust me, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.97,0:11:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here! You ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.51,0:11:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.77,0:11:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.29,0:11:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,three!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.17,0:11:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.00,0:11:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Take us to the beach!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.57,0:11:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't even stop the bus.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.90,0:11:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm shocked.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.32,0:11:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,More than shocked, I'm pissed!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.20,0:12:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, Megumi, you swore it'd work! \NNow we just look like idiots!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.78,0:12:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, all right. \NLet's just go change already.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.67,0:12:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So soft.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.75,0:12:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{hehe / Whoa!}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.69,0:12:12.98,Top,,0,0,0,,You've got a pretty solid ass there. \NHow about the other one?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.98,0:12:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Pet.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You pervert! {chikan = molester}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.32,0:12:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Boobies secured! {???????? no clue what's that second word}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.30,0:12:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.60,0:12:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get mad just 'cause \Nsome guy touched your butt
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.25,0:12:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're out here\N half-naked on the street. {/in swimsuits}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.65,0:12:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Cut it out, you creep!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.86,0:12:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you what \Na real man tastes like.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.29,0:12:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneak out... {?????? no clue what's this zukko but sounds like some onoma for "sneakily" or maybe "standing up/hard"}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.34,0:12:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Megumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.55,0:12:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your turn now.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.30,0:12:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.22,0:13:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How big is it?! {?????? wouldn't expect her to praise him in this situation but idk what else it could mean}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.24,0:13:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts! You're gonna break me!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.64,0:13:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take it slow back at my place,\Nreal slow and sticky. {lit: have a nice, sticky, gooey time}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.48,0:13:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha! Caught me a couple of pretty ones!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.25,0:13:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop! {matte}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.38,0:13:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! {oroshite}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.75,0:13:14.73,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.44,0:13:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yoshimoto, how about we hit the beach tomorrow?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.12,0:13:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The beach?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.95,0:13:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, the beach!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.68,0:13:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the blazing sun, \Nhot girls in bikinis splashing in the waves,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.78,0:13:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and when night falls, sex on the sand \Ntill you forget the sting of your sunburn! {Was "the burn of", but sounded off so close to sunburn.}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.13,0:13:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That{\i0} beach.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.44,0:13:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I'll never get how you can talk about
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.53,0:13:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that stuff at full volume \Nwalking down the street.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.93,0:13:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, man, who cares. \NLet's just go!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.20,0:13:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My horoscope says tomorrow's \Nmy lucky day for picking up girls!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.97,0:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To my place! {??????????? no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.92,0:13:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Yarita?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.98,0:13:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yoshimoto and Tajima?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.86,0:13:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did he just say "Yarita"?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.76,0:14:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, you mean it could be {\i1}that{\i0} Yarita?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.69,0:14:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yarita the Jackhammer? {bukkomu is "to drive (something) into; to strike into; to hammer in" - safe to assume it's about how he fucks}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.10,0:14:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If he keeps at it, \Nhe's totally gonna break us in two! {lit: break the important part/thing - referring to their genitals I assume}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.13,0:14:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder, his thing \Nwas the size of a damn horse. {like a horse's dick}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.01,0:14:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where'd you find those girls? \NSnatched them from a pool somewhere?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.68,0:14:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice haul. Gonna have\N yourself some fun, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.23,0:14:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, that's Yukari and Megumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.67,0:14:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.26,0:14:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If he does it, he'll tear me apart!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.10,0:14:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you save us, we'll go out with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.89,0:14:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.77,0:14:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me carry them, \Nand I'll let you have a turn too.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.12,0:14:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You traitors! \NHow could you side with that bastard?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.61,0:14:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we promise to go out with you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.96,0:14:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go, damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.57,0:14:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your idea of going out is probably \Nhaving some tea together, at best.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.05,0:14:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We know how you girls twist words.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.49,0:14:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, better take what's right in front of us \Nthan dream about a possible screw.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.15,0:14:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.44,0:14:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Save us from these perverts, somebody! {???????}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.26,0:15:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.07,0:15:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so lively! {??????????????? no clue, probably something about her pussy}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.10,0:15:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that feel, that smell... been a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.66,0:15:12.42,Top,,0,0,0,,Ugh... Digging holes in the summer heat \Nain't easy, Nemuro.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.42,0:15:14.21,Top,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.21,0:15:17.29,Top,,0,0,0,,It's your fault we got booted \Nfrom the pachinko parlor! {/fired}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.29,0:15:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't punched the manager, \NI'd be chillin' under the A/C, smokin' right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.78,0:15:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! If it isn't Kariya and Nemuro.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.20,0:15:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Still full of energy in this damn heat, huh? {sei ga deru = working hard}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.03,0:15:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yarita?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.14,0:15:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.25,0:15:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tajima and Yoshimoto too!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.27,0:15:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Still full of energy in this damn heat, huh? {same sei ga deru as earlier}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.80,0:15:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yarita invited us out, can you believe it?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.92,0:15:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna come too?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.71,0:15:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to sweat it out \Ninside a woman than out here. {another rephrase of sei ga deru}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.67,0:16:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, these exhibitionists were strutting around the street in swimsuits,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.04,0:16:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,so the more guys the merrier! {meaning "the more guys fuck her, the happier she is"}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.61,0:16:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, boys!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.97,0:16:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell yeah, let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.49,0:16:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi, this is all your fault!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.97,0:16:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't suggested we wear swimsuits, \Nnone of this would've happened!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.84,0:16:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I knew it would make \Nall the other guys around here that riled up!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.90,0:16:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done for! \NFive of them already. {lit: being fucked by five}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.20,0:16:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had more than\N three at once before!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.60,0:16:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yarita's the real problem here!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.76,0:16:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They say if he hammers you, \Nyou won't walk right for a month! {buchikomareru - the word from his nickname}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.86,0:16:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A whole month?! \NThat'll ruin my summer!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.44,0:16:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta find a chance to run for it, fast. {lit: if there's an opening, we have to run for it}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.20,0:16:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass 'em, pass 'em, let's take turns! \NPass, pass, yeah, that's it! {lit: gang rape, gang rape, let's get along while we gang rape, gang rape, gang rape, there we go}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.47,0:16:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.56,0:17:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird. Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.46,0:17:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess they got pissed \Nand went to the pool or something.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.74,0:17:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! {aniki}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.22,0:17:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takashi, you seen \NYukari and Megumi around?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.62,0:17:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, saw them near \Nthe cleaning firm on Second Street. {literal, probably some shop that offers professional cleaning? Feels like dry cleaners?}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.52,0:17:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, there?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.68,0:17:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't done talking.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.91,0:17:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, the girls are getting away!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.29,0:17:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How the hell did you idiots screw that up?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-They kicked us in the balls!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.19,0:17:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbasses! You let a couple of girls \Nget the drop on you!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.85,0:17:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Later! {abayo - adieu / see you later}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.16,0:17:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.46,0:17:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Like those snails \Ncould ever catch up with us! {lit: those slow-paced guys are chasing us?}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.40,0:17:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even the cops could catch us! {specifically "police officer" so she means on foot}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.32,0:17:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming after us like maniacs! {lit: with great impetus}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.62,0:17:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How the hell can they run that fast?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.79,0:18:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't waste your breath. At this rate... {??? nc what she means by keeping quiet}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.98,0:18:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...w-we'll definitely...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.56,0:18:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,get caught!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.65,0:18:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, found you two at last!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.57,0:18:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.03,0:18:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell? Why'd you appear like that all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.62,0:18:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Never mind that! \NThose guys were about to assault us!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.39,0:18:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.42,0:18:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, R-Ryota-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.52,0:18:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So you idiots finally snapped from the heat \Nand decided to turn to sex crime, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.58,0:18:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.44,0:18:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it all wrong! \NWe were just helping out, that's all...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.36,0:18:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you catch them or not?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.93,0:18:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ryota!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.74,0:18:38.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,F-Fuck, he appeared at the worst possible time. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.24,0:18:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yarita, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.74,0:18:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After all the warnings I gave you \Nback in the day, you haven't learned
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.13,0:18:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and still treat women like toys?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.76,0:18:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I'd never call them toys or anything...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.38,0:18:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If any one of you here is even {\i1}thinking{\i0}\N of laying a hand on these girls,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.76,0:18:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,then you'd better disappear before I count to three.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.13,0:18:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do that, and I'll pretend I didn't see a thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.20,0:18:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.42,0:19:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't expect a thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.04,0:19:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't ignored us in broad daylight, \Nthis never would've happened!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.39,0:19:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, I've got something for you girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.48,0:19:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's for Megumi,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.39,0:19:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one's for Yukari.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.05,0:19:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.02,0:19:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Swimsuits. Women's stuff sure doesn't come cheap.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.73,0:19:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But why?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.59,0:19:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I just don't like the ones \Nyou're wearing now.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hop in. \NWe're going to the beach!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.55,0:19:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The beach?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.52,0:19:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If we floor it now, \Nwe'll make it to the sea before nightfall.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.14,0:19:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning we'll hit the water \Nin those suits and swim our hearts out.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.78,0:19:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.77,0:19:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing beats going to the beach \Nin summer, huh, Takashi?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.38,0:19:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but... is this really okay? \NYou practically hijacked the bus. {meaning that he's supposed to return it to depot but he takes it away}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.60,0:19:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's gonna miss one bus.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.71,0:20:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.45,0:20:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi, don't sweat the small stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.09,0:20:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This bus is all ours, a private trip!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.52,0:20:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi, why didn't you\N bring Yuki-chan along?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.71,0:20:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I get tired of going out \Nwith the same girl all the time. {lit: the same flavor / taste}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.88,0:20:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling Yuki-chan on you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.84,0:20:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Boss, just this once...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.99,0:20:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, no way.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.64,0:20:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You kids should stick \Nto fooling around with each other.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.91,0:20:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. We adults will have our own fun. \NIsn't that right, Ryota-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.90,0:20:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the sweet, fiery fun \Nonly adults know. Right, Ryota-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.84,0:20:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ryota-san, you really are the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.00,0:20:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wonderful, Ryota-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.37,0:20:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, tonight, let's play harem
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.20,0:20:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,with Ryota-san and Yukari!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.66,0:20:49.76,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Harem. Harem...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.11,0:20:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds perfect!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.76,0:20:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start the prelude\N right now, Ryota-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.44,0:20:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what about me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.80,0:20:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids should go poop \Nand hit the sack, right, Yukari?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.42,0:21:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, bedtime for kids.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.30,0:21:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Aw, come on! I'm not a kid!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.12,0:21:13.23,Thought,,0,0,0,,Fine then, if that's how it is, \NI'll go flirt with some cute young thing myself!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.04,0:21:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Ryota-san, please pull over for a sec!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.05,0:21:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, miss! \NWanna come to the beach with us?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.73,0:21:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on! \NLet's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.70,0:21:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I'm too embarrassed!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.63,0:21:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.50,0:21:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply adorable!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.37,0:21:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, really, I'm embarrassed!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.43,0:21:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, get on the bus \Nmade just for cute girls like you, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.82,0:21:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm embarrassed, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.18,0:21:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,kinda happy!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.46,0:21:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.14,0:21:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how cute, he's blushing!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.01,0:21:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit! Takashi, you and your girl shouldn't be shy. Go for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.21,0:21:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.09,0:22:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.89,0:22:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch. What a damn nuisance this bus is.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.41,0:22:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's blow right past it.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.33,0:22:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's a bus even driving on a road like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.47,0:22:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the way, turtle-bus! {?? nc what's that kameko but something about turtles}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.15,0:22:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh-heh. Turtle-bus, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.29,0:22:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! They could've just passed quietly, but no.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.02,0:22:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we'll have to show them \Nwho the real turtle is.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.36,0:22:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Go all out!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.22,0:22:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Floor it!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.59,0:22:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we can gun it full throttle now!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.26,0:22:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Think Masato can keep up?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.68,0:22:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Masato!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.06,0:22:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Behind you!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.17,0:22:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, seriously?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.80,0:22:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How the hell's he hitting that speed \Non a mountain road?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.09,0:22:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Morons! Step on it!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:45.50,0:22:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pedal to the floor!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:47.50,0:22:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't wanna end up tumbling \Ninto the valley, so we're ahead! Like that! {?????????????? I hear "*** falling to the bottom of the valley would be bad, so it's about time I've made it to the front"}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:57.40,0:22:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:58.61,0:23:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel it! Ecstasy!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:04.78,0:23:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling ecstatic too!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:06.88,0:23:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.05,0:23:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Polish your driving, rookie!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.21,0:23:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What a maniac.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.79,0:23:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what the hell are you doing, \Npulling up over there? {???? nc what's that aoiutsu}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:21.63,0:23:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kawai-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.97,0:23:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takashi!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.54,0:23:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss gets all the fun! Geez...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.91,0:23:36.66,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Let's have some fun ourselves!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:38.58,0:23:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a boat out as well!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.05,0:23:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nah, sorry, boats make me seasick.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.40,0:23:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, poor thing. Then I'll comfort you \Nand help you get over it. Come on! {lit: nurse you}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.50,0:23:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding me. \NI always draw the short straw!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:58.71,0:24:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Takashi-san, you're so innocent!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.07,0:24:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think\N you're doing over there?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.35,0:24:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the one who was\N rolling in that bus? {korogashi}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.47,0:24:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if I am?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:13.70,0:24:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, these guys here said your bus \Nnearly ran them off the road,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.08,0:24:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so I figured I'd stop by and have a word. {/say hello}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.07,0:24:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, Takashi-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.24,0:24:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, are those your friends?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:27.98,0:24:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the scary face?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:30.83,0:24:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't be mean to Takashi-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:37.81,0:24:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Back off, ugly pig!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:39.71,0:24:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Raising your hand against a woman \Nwho's not even involved? You're pathetic, man!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:45.99,0:24:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:49.31,0:24:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawai-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:51.87,0:24:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you're tough, huh? {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:57.87,0:24:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:01.93,0:25:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Takashi-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:03.44,0:25:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You swine!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:06.86,0:25:10.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,S-So cool! He's fighting for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:14.26,0:25:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi-san, here,\N help me up now, my knight!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:19.17,0:25:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're such a tease!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:23.42,0:25:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go, idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:24.86,0:25:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be shy!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:26.58,0:25:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop following me! {??????}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:28.34,0:25:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Takashi! \NLook at him go!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:31.95,0:25:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wild scene, huh! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:33.76,0:25:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:44.21,0:25:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukari and Megumi sure\N are taking their time.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:47.88,0:25:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we went a little too far last night?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:56.03,0:25:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Takashi's gone too.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:59.48,0:26:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, guess he was up all night too. {lit: doing it till mornign}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:03.38,0:26:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boss! Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:05.49,0:26:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:06.20,0:26:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! My knight!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:09.53,0:26:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:11.36,0:26:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two never quit. \NHang in there, Takashi!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:17.58,0:26:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:30.74,0:26:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, did you buy these \Nfrom an adult shop?!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:34.73,0:26:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't swim in things like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:08.07,0:27:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Look at this, Tajima!\NI've got a new car!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:11.80,0:27:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A new car? Yoshimoto, \Nsince when could you afford that?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:17.23,0:27:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike you, I don't blow\N my cash on good food. {eating heavily; hearty eating; binge eating; gluttony}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:20.10,0:27:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been saving up bit by bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:22.74,0:27:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking back to that summer \Nwhen I was eighteen...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:25.62,0:27:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought a used Cedric for 150,000 yen, \Nchallenged Ryota with it,
Dialogue: 10,0:27:29.11,0:27:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and drowned it in the Arakawa River.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:31.65,0:27:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The long days when I had to make do \Nwith the shop's pickup truck
Dialogue: 10,0:27:34.88,0:27:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and bum rides in your filthy cars...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:37.95,0:27:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All those ups and downs, while still spending too much on women... It was all for today's sake. {lit: the days of shop's light truck and freeloading at your and other underlings' dirty cars continued enduring, to effect or to no effect, without decreasing money spent on women, it brings us to today - dunno what's that "effect" part}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:44.02,0:27:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's nice, but all in all, \Nthis baby must've cost around four mil.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:48.53,0:27:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So how much was the down payment? {down payment; deposit​}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:50.96,0:27:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A mil. The rest's on a thirty-six–month plan.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:54.49,0:27:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A mil?!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:57.68,0:28:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Didn't know you'd saved up that much. \NMan, that's crazy.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:01.45,0:28:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But the monthly payments \Nmust still be pretty steep, no?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:05.73,0:28:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tajima, a real man's gotta take on some debt if he wants to grow big.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:12.32,0:28:14.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,He's not acting like his usual self.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:14.80,0:28:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, first ride!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:16.76,0:28:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I swore I'd only let my girl ride shotgun,
Dialogue: 10,0:28:20.16,0:28:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but since you've always had my back,\N I'll make an exception this once.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:26.23,0:28:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure I'm not the only person you let ride here, all right? {lit: if it doesn't become my exclusive use seat, it's good - think he means "make sure you drive women in it at all, and not just me"}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:29.73,0:28:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, here we go!\NToday marks my new beginning.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:34.44,0:28:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:41.47,0:28:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, this feels incredible!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:04.57,0:29:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yoshimoto...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:10.79,0:29:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wrong, idiot, wrong, wrong!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:14.87,0:29:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yoshimoto, hang in there! You okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:21.28,0:29:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I said stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:23.53,0:29:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not, Yuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:27.25,0:29:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just seeing your hips move like that,\NI can't hold back anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:32.40,0:29:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you're impossible... \Nin the middle of the day, even.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:38.61,0:29:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, just a quickie, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:42.22,0:29:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's make it count!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:44.10,0:29:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh geez, Takashi, you're so bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:47.77,0:29:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, here I come, Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:56.48,0:29:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Taka-chan! Taka-chan, right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:02.55,0:30:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:03.54,0:30:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Taka-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:11.71,0:30:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it inside...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:14.38,0:30:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Here it comes!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:15.48,0:30:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Taka-chan, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:38.78,0:30:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Taka-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:41.45,0:30:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:47.72,0:30:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's how it is, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:51.41,0:30:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He trashed Yoshimoto's brand-new four–million–yen car,
Dialogue: 10,0:30:54.54,0:30:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and then he took Takashi's Yuki-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:57.77,0:31:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just please find him, fast!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:00.11,0:31:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forgive that driver, no way in hell.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:03.01,0:31:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:04.36,0:31:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing this for your sake!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:07.71,0:31:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan not wearing any panties \Nis my only motivation. {lit: i'm doing this out of concern for nopan yuki}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:18.53,0:31:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:19.92,0:31:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:21.46,0:31:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gonna happen to Yuki, boss?!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:24.16,0:31:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit your whining!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:26.22,0:31:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the bastards want\N a head-on showdown.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:44.68,0:31:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:47.18,0:31:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys okay?!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:50.58,0:31:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Barely...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:56.57,0:31:59.28,Top,,0,0,0,,Oh! Akada Shigeki?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:59.65,0:32:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Akada? Then the one driving \Nmust be Aoyagi Gunji, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:04.27,0:32:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that bastard Aoyagi's \Nthe one who wrecked my car!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:12.46,0:32:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:15.18,0:32:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:16.31,0:32:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the beating last time. {kawaigatte - primary meaning is "to take care/to treat kindly" but wtf? I assume he means it ironically here}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:19.75,0:32:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to return the favor today!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:23.80,0:32:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:25.30,0:32:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, thanks to a hostage, \NI won't lose to you. {lit: this time, we've got a hostage on our side}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:28.48,0:32:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So think twice before you make a move! {??? dunno what he means}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:35.41,0:32:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,One wrong move and this girl will meet her fate.\NI can throw her off anytime! See?!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:41.54,0:32:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop! Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:47.62,0:32:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing \Nat a time like this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:51.78,0:32:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?! Peeping is all you care about? \NOh, gimme a break! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:56.18,0:32:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have told you \Nshe's going commando, dammit! {nopan}
Dialogue: 10,0:33:01.65,0:33:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how should I have fun \Nwith this chick first?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:10.85,0:33:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Taka-chan...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:16.12,0:33:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Akada! Lay one filthy finger \Non Yuki and I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:20.95,0:33:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi! This is what you get \Nfor hanging around Ryota all the time.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:26.27,0:33:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've gotta blame someone, blame him!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:28.59,0:33:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:30.87,0:33:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:35.79,0:33:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:37.87,0:33:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:33:38.74,0:33:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl's got a pretty nice rack, huh? \NGuess I'll strip her panties off next.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:48.28,0:33:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:50.22,0:33:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Violating a girl like this out here...\NNow that's a thrill.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:55.02,0:33:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:56.83,0:33:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:58.60,0:34:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, what the hell. \NShe's not even wearing panties!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:03.29,0:34:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What a slut, this one.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:05.50,0:34:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll drag her through the shopping district like this,
Dialogue: 10,0:34:08.67,0:34:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,lift her skirt, and let everyone have a look! Whaddya say, huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:12.33,0:34:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, give us your ass!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:16.76,0:34:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let them see it all first!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:19.77,0:34:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No! S-Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:21.25,0:34:23.98,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Come on, up we go now...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:25.09,0:34:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:26.23,0:34:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There, like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:28.00,0:34:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Taka-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:33.72,0:34:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there, there!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:36.20,0:34:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:39.52,0:34:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:41.85,0:34:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! If you don't want to watch me \Nshoving my manhood into this girl, {lit: slamming my thing into ...}
Dialogue: 10,0:34:47.17,0:34:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi, hit Ryota!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:51.53,0:34:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit the driver, Ryota!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:53.97,0:34:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:54.73,0:34:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it, or I'll ravish her right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:58.88,0:35:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi, do what he says!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:01.30,0:35:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But how could I? \NHitting my own boss...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:06.25,0:35:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, what are you waiting for?!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:08.64,0:35:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up or I'll do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:13.13,0:35:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you hesitating?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:15.17,0:35:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi, if I see him screw Yuki-chan, \NI'll burn that sight into my brain
Dialogue: 10,0:35:20.37,0:35:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and jerk off to it later!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:23.66,0:35:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:25.87,0:35:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:27.57,0:35:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:31.91,0:35:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, Takashi! \NNow keep hitting him. Don't stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:37.16,0:35:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:40.97,0:35:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep punching!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:47.80,0:35:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too damn good!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:49.61,0:35:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it feel, Ryota, \Ngetting beaten down like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:55.39,0:35:58.85,Top,,0,0,0,,Keep going! Beat him to death!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:00.02,0:36:03.90,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shit, he's having the time of his life up there.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:06.98,0:36:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard, cut it out already!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:09.49,0:36:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:10.25,0:36:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't "Huh?" me!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:11.86,0:36:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:12.91,0:36:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he urged Takashi himself... \NYou don't wanna cross that man. {????????? only hear "said himself ..."}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:16.79,0:36:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know... {??????????}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:18.80,0:36:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! The wheel... {unten = driving (a vehicle)}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:24.25,0:36:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you really keep up, Yoshimoto? {korogasu}{probably means "can you handle catching up to him on a bus"}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:26.59,0:36:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:27.60,0:36:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That son of a bitch totaled \Nmy brand-new four–million–yen car! {??????? nc what's that kojitora}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:30.72,0:36:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for Yuki-chan, \Nwe could've rammed right into them!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:35.17,0:36:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,See? 'Cause of you, they can't \Nmake a move, only tail us helplessly!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:44.69,0:36:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:45.95,0:36:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:49.21,0:36:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing,
Dialogue: 10,0:36:51.11,0:36:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you bitch?!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:53.30,0:36:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:55.55,0:36:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:56.36,0:37:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You broad! \NI don't care if you die now! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:00.30,0:37:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:03.26,0:37:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Bitch! {konoyaro}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:04.16,0:37:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:08.17,0:37:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck you! {??? probably "kurae = die/drop dead"}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:11.34,0:37:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You whore! {?? yaree? dunno what he means}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:12.46,0:37:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, Akada!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:24.64,0:37:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi! Catch her!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:28.77,0:37:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:30.23,0:37:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch! Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:34.69,0:37:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, I lost the hostage.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:38.32,0:37:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoyagi, isn't it about time \Nto give them a head-on showdown? {meaning ram them}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:42.03,0:37:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch. You're having all the fun yourself.\NYou could at least get a license, dammit! {probably means "all because I do have a license and you don't"}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:48.48,0:37:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! He rammed us?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:50.50,0:37:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna pay for this, you bastards! {lit: prepare yourselves}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:53.41,0:37:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna dump you into the sea \Ntogether with your truck! {meaning "You can stay, we'll do it with you inside"}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:56.43,0:38:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! Aoyagi, swing us around. \NHit them head-on!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:02.30,0:38:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No can do! We got rear-ended earlier, \Nso the brakes got soft from the shock! {?? dunno how that works but that's what he says}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:06.95,0:38:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:08.16,0:38:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't make me laugh! \NThey're trying to run! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:10.73,0:38:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can outrun me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:16.11,0:38:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Akada, at this rate, \Nwe'll fly straight into the ocean!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:20.67,0:38:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Ryota won't be able \Nto stop in time at this speed!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:23.84,0:38:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're going down, \Nwe're taking them with us!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:27.46,0:38:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:31.54,0:38:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Ryota-san! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:35.50,0:38:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We're not gonna make it! {/there's not enough time/distance}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:38.38,0:38:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, I've got this.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:47.14,0:38:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, we're going down! {???????}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:48.99,0:38:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the fuck just happened?! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:50.75,0:38:54.08,Overlap,,0,0,0,,We're sinking, Akada! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:54.61,0:38:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's get Yuki-chan to a hospital!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:57.27,0:38:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:01.53,0:39:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Yuki-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:05.05,0:39:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:06.55,0:39:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard hurt you so bad... You, a girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:09.81,0:39:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, I only lost a lousy \Nfour–million–yen car...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:15.24,0:39:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Ryota-san, stop, stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:17.69,0:39:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta catch those bastards \Nand make them pay for my new car: four mil!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:21.98,0:39:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Treating Yuki-chan's wounds comes first!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:24.53,0:39:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You're letting them escape! {/run away}
Dialogue: 5,0:39:39.24,0:39:45.18,Song,,0,0,0,,Someone trusted me with their life{"Korogashi Ryouta no Uta" by Hidaka Masato; going by ear, copying from episode 1}
Dialogue: 5,0:39:45.18,0:39:50.65,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll give them mine
Dialogue: 5,0:39:50.65,0:39:53.58,Song,,0,0,0,,In the rear view, the city shines
Dialogue: 5,0:39:53.58,0:39:56.62,Song,,0,0,0,,With the eyes of starving beasts
Dialogue: 5,0:39:57.04,0:40:07.15,Song,,0,0,0,,Ambitious guys, they don't care for your opinion
Dialogue: 5,0:40:07.15,0:40:18.91,Song,,0,0,0,,That's how I roll, roll, roll, roll, Rolling Ryota
